code: @Before public void setUp() throws Exception {     endpoint = new MetricsEndpoint(null, null, registry, MetricsType.HISTOGRAM, METRICS_NAME).     inOrder = Mockito.inOrder(registry). }
@After public void tearDown() throws Exception {     inOrder.verifyNoMoreInteractions(). }

@Test public void testHistogramEndpoint() throws Exception {     assertThat(endpoint, is(notNullValue())).     assertThat(endpoint.getRegistry(), is(registry)).     assertThat(endpoint.getMetricsName(), is(METRICS_NAME)). }

@Test public void testCreateProducer() throws Exception {     Producer producer = endpoint.createProducer().     assertThat(producer, is(notNullValue())).     assertThat(producer, is(instanceOf(HistogramProducer.class))). }
@Test public void testGetValue() throws Exception {     assertThat(endpoint.getValue(), is(nullValue())). }
@Test public void testSetValue() throws Exception {     assertThat(endpoint.getValue(), is(nullValue())).     endpoint.setValue(VALUE).     assertThat(endpoint.getValue(), is(VALUE)). }
